">
<span style=3D"font-size:11pt; font-family:Calibri,sans-serif; color:rgb(31=
,73,125)">Umesh Malhotra is a serial entrepreneur with experience of workin=
g across a range of markets, and product categories. He has sold and servic=
ed customers in USA, Europe and India
 and has significant experience working with NGOs and consumers in Indian v=
illages. He has worked in product categories like IT services, Restaurants,=
 Education Retail, and Social Entrepreneurship. His organization Hippocampu=
s is known globally as a game changer
 in education for the poor. &nbsp;&nbsp;He is a Ashoka and Asia Society fel=
low and is a graduate of IIT Madras.</span></p>
